&lt;p&gt;Have you ever dreamed of joining an exciting team? Do you want a job where people and quality of service are the organisation’s top priority? If you answer yes to the above we have an exciting opportunity for you within the Continuing Healthcare Team. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for a ‘can do’ person who likes to challenge themselves. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;An opportunity has arisen for an administration post within the Continuing Healthcare Team on a short term basis. You should be a dynamic, effective communicator especially on the telephone, have good organisational skills and be able to take minutes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will suit a high calibre individual who is organised and wants to work as part of a team who are passionate about improving the quality of care for patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Helen Biss&lt;/p&gt;
